Achievements.Name: Welcome to Just Dance 2015!
Achievements.Description: Complete your first song.

Achievements.Name: Finding your feet
Achievements.Description: Get 3 stars on a song.

Achievements.Name: Just Dance Warm-up
Achievements.Description: Get 3 stars on 5 different songs.

Achievements.Name: NAILED it!
Achievements.Description: Get 5 stars on a song.

Achievements.Name: Born to Perform
Achievements.Description: Get 5 stars on 5 different songs.

Achievements.Name: Solid Gold Performance
Achievements.Description: Perform all Gold Moves in a song (No Mash-Ups)

Achievements.Name: You're GOLD, Gold!
Achievements.Description: Perform all Gold Moves in 5 songs (No Mash-Ups)

Achievements.Name: It's all Good!
Achievements.Description: Perform only Good Moves or better in a song (No Mash-Ups)

Achievements.Name: You've got a friend in me....
Achievements.Description: Finish 5 songs with 2 or more players dancing.

Achievements.Name: Party Animal
Achievements.Description: Finish 20 songs with 2 or more players dancing.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Finish!
Achievements.Description: Get a Perfect on the last move of a song (No Mash-Ups).

Achievements.Name: The perfect combo
Achievements.Description: Get 10 Perfect moves in a row in any song.

Achievements.Name: Got those moves like Jagger
Achievements.Description: Complete a song with 90% or more Perfect moves (No Mash-Ups).

Achievements.Name: Dance Crew
Achievements.Description: Get 3 stars with all four players on any song with 4 Dancers.

Achievements.Name: Funky Four!
Achievements.Description: Get 5 stars with all four players on any song with 4 Dancers.

Achievements.Name: The Dynamic Duo
Achievements.Description: On a song with 2 Dancers get 5 stars on both dancers.

Achievements.Name: Out of this world!
Achievements.Description: Get 3 stars on all songs (No Alternate versions or Mash-Ups).

Achievements.Name: The ULTIMATE Just Dance fan
Achievements.Description: Get 5 stars on all Songs (No Alternate versions or Mash-Ups).

Achievements.Name: Just starting out...
Achievements.Description: Complete a 3 Dancer song with 3 or more players.

Achievements.Name: Bring on the wall!
Achievements.Description: Access the JD Wall and see what's going on in Just Dance 2015.

Achievements.Name: Variety Act
Achievements.Description: Dance one song of these map types: 1, 2, 3 and 4 coaches.

Achievements.Name: First purchase!
Achievements.Description: Spend 10 Mojo.

Achievements.Name: Loaded!
Achievements.Description: Spend 50 Mojo.

Achievements.Name: Make it RAIN!
Achievements.Description: Spend 200 Mojo.

Achievements.Name: I want it ALL!
Achievements.Description: Unlock all Avatars and Mash-Ups (no DLC or Uplay).

Achievements.Name: All your dance are belong to us!
Achievements.Description: Get 5 stars on Holding Out for a Hero.

Achievements.Name: Forever alone
Achievements.Description: Dance to a 2 Dancer song on your own.

Achievements.Name: The definition of 'Insanity'
Achievements.Description: Dance 'You Spin Me Round (Like a Record)' 3 times in a row.

Achievements.Name: Gonna make you Sweat!
Achievements.Description: Play a playlist with Kcal tracking toggled on.

Achievements.Name: Power Playlist
Achievements.Description: Play a 40 minute playlist.

Achievements.Name: Everybody Dance Now!
Achievements.Description: Complete a dance with 6 players.

Achievements.Name: Get your high 5 a day!
Achievements.Description: Perform a high 5 gesture with another player.

Achievements.Name: Say CHEESE!
Achievements.Description: Smile on the Autodance Screen.

Achievements.Name: Everyday I'm Shuffling
Achievements.Description: Use the effects shuffle button to apply an effect to your Autodance video.
